title: Patrice O'Neal - The Complete Collection
description:
This is the complete stand-up and radio works of comedian Patrice O'Neal.

Contents:

Standup:

All video stand up includes additional audio copies divided into tracks for easy listening.

2003 - Comedy Central Presents
2003 - The Patrice O'Neal Roast (audio only)
2004 - Live at the Comedy Store in Hollywood, Calif.
2005 - One Night Stand
2005 - The Lost Files Circa 2005
2011 - Elephant in the Room (plus extras)
2011 - Mr. P
2011 - Unreleased
A collection of 16 stand up appearances throughout his career, mostly ripped from YouTube.

Interviews:

A collection of 21 audio and video interviews and television appearances from various sources, mostly ripped from YouTube.

Radio: 

All of Patrice's Opie and Anthony appearances - 146 recordings
The Black Phillip Show - 13 recordings

Other:

The Patrice O'Neal Show - All 27 episodes and extra features
